%% Diagram: optimistic update with server reconciliation
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as UI / store
    participant API as Server
    participant DB as Source of truth

    User->>UI: drop (drag commit)
    UI->>UI: snapshot prevState
    UI->>UI: apply optimistic reorder
    UI-->>User: render new order

    UI->>API: PATCH /items {newOrder}
    API->>DB: persist + validate
    alt success
        DB-->>API: ok (canonical pos)
        API-->>UI: 200 + canonical order
        UI->>UI: reconcile (replace optimistic<br/>state with server response)
    else conflict / 4xx / 5xx / network
        API-->>UI: error or timeout
        UI->>UI: rollback to prevState
        UI-->>User: toast "Failed to save"
    end

    Note over UI,API: Conflict resolution = server wins.<br/>Concurrent edits land via WS broadcast.
